{"tid":1283370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[永遠置頂]  實測！！！ Whatsapp, Instagram, Facebook 上傳唔到關於反送中嘅圖","createTime":"2019-07-03T19:14:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T15:54:20.000Z","uid":30391,"like":90,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"cda8f0e54496a7b2e9d9d9fefbe7f9ce34ea5fa7","tid":1283370,"uid":30391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T19:14:31.000Z","msg":"唔知道有無人發現<br />\n但係絕對有理由懷疑 <br />\n<br />\n由於同朋友都認為佢load咁耐都load 唔到<br />\n個原因係咪因爲佢需要時間去detect幅相係咩黎<br />\n<br />\n所以我做咗幾次測試<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eGJEjiQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeGJEjiQ.png&h=32617053&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢張對比應該明顯少少<br />\n上一秒send 到 党嘅野<br />\n下一秒試send 關於反送中嘅資料send 唔出去<br />\n只係1 秒嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n⚠️⚠️<br />\n然後我試埋可唔可以upload 上ig story<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bKodoL1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbKodoL1.png&h=f4323384&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一次係失敗嘅<br />\n<br />\n然後我試多幾次都唔得<br />\n<br />\n我就試下遮哂下面個兩張圖<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NyWZjj1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNyWZjj1.png&h=0b7d9298&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇下右下角個facebook share<br />\n成功upload 到啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我即刻起哂雞皮"},{"pid":"96344bd2008489ea7e01bbab8f60e53759391b4e","tid":1283370,"uid":30391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T19:16:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"31e9f310